[I] Download Youtube Videos

[T] youtubedr is a video downloader.

[U] https://github.com/kkdai/youtube

[A] Evan Lin
[M] The T2 Project <t2@t2-project.org>

[C] extra/tool
[F] CROSS

[L] MIT
[V] 2.10.6

[D] 52ac7273498855f6bd94ed61c0e7b8ddf4e58b6d92e7d3e4ba96dbe7 youtube-2.10.6.tar.gz https://github.com/kkdai/youtube/archive/v2.10.6/

. $base/package/*/*/go-conf.in
var_append goconfopt ' ' "-o youtubedr ./cmd/youtubedr"
hook_add postmake 5 "cp -vf youtubedr $root$bindir/"
